					<h2 class="posttitle"><a href="http://pettradeworld.com/2010/01/scruffs%c2%ae-open-days-17th-%e2%80%93-18th-february-10am-%e2%80%93-4pm/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Scruffs® Open Days 17th – 18th February, 10am – 4pm">Scruffs® Open Days 17th – 18th February, 10am – 4pm</a></h2>
					<p class="date"><span class="byline">Jan 7 2010 in <a href="http://pettradeworld.com/category/blog/" title="View all posts in News" rel="category tag">News</a> <em>by <a href="http://naidre" title="Visit naidre&#8217;s website" rel="external">naidre</a></em></span></p>
						<div class="entry">
								
							<p>Scruffs® are hosting an open day event at their purpose built showroom, located in Manchester. The event is open to trade buyers, giving them an opportunity to view the extensive Scruffs® pet bedding collection. Buyers will be able to see new lines for the first time and take advantage of promotional offers.</p>
<p>One of the new products on show will be the much-anticipated ‘Grizzly Bear Bed’ an enormous paw bed measuring 130cm in diameter. Visitors will also be able to view the new 2010 collection of Tramps Cat Activity Centres, finished in a luxurious Snow Leopard plush fur.</p>
<p>The Scruffs showroom is located at Manchester House, Rothwell, Street, Walkden, Worsley, Manchester M28 3WG and will be open from 10am – 4pm on the 17th and 18th February. It is not necessary to make an appointment, however if you would like to talk to a sales representative in advance please contact their sales office on 0161 702 5060 or e-mail sales@petslovescruffs.com</p>
						</div>
